8785::$$$message_0087_0000_0000$$$::Classes end, and it's time to go home.[lr]::
8786::$$$message_0087_0000_0001$$$::I can't wander around because I have work today.[lr]::
8787::$$$message_0087_0000_0002$$$::I shouldn't do anything at school. I should head straight to the neighboring town, but...::

